environment.description: Environnement créé sur la base de l'environment profile HipDatalakeDev
environment.name: datalake-dev-test1

userParameters.description: Use this input to customize the name of the consuming glue database, that is created for this environment and used to link approved data assets from other accounts, so that they can be queried by the tools in this environment.
Use this input to customize the name of the producing glue database, that is created for this environment and used to create new assets that can then be published into the catalog for discovery.
Use this input to customize the name of the Athena Workgroup that is created and used to store query history of queries that are run.
